Helios-App-ThumbnailGenerator version 0.01
==========================================

Helios::App::ThumbnailGenerator is a small Helios application that 
uses Image::Magick to generate thumbnails for images.  It's 
intended primary uses are to provide a service for other applications 
to hand off thumbnail generation duties, and to distribute the 
workload of generating thumbnails for large batches of images across 
multiple worker processes or hosts.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Helios 2.80 or later
    Image::Magick 6.6.9
    Image::Magick::Thumbnail 0.06


